     <p>The wage gap between female and male actors is criminal. In many cases, actors will be in the same "tier", but the female wil only be paid a fraction of what her male colleague is recieving.<br> The question constantly asked, is, "What can a woman in film DO to get paid the same as my male colleague?" Here are some statistics and pointers to help you become a vital part in closing the gap.</p><br>
